    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "1WVcughiS/z29R5i/XTtaEW5pEUfAiHqABN//ynlsrs=",
    "originContent": "There are two variables that control which directory Marsdev is built and installed:",
    "translatedContent": "Hay dos variables que controlan en qué directorio se construye e instala Marsdev:"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "qY9wE7M1CedlXSeLsQCEFRY5iplaYxsw29EfJgyuKno=",
    "originContent": " - `MARS_BUILD_DIR` = (REPOSITORY_ROOT)/mars",
    "translatedContent": " - `MARS_BUILD_DIR` = (REPOSITORY_ROOT)/mars"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "Gfc2o+uuMpwYiwQWs7FbXUd7hnKFi8QEo4bMMcdBtU0=",
    "originContent": " - `MARS_INSTALL_DIR` = /opt/toolchains/mars",
    "translatedContent": " - `MARS_INSTALL_DIR` = /opt/toolchains/mars"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "PyM4218N3jRnC7zR9rUDGDc5E0iRVW0jh238DtyWx9s=",
    "originContent": "If you wish to change the location of either, use an export command like this:",
    "translatedContent": "Si desea cambiar la ubicación de cualquiera de ellos, use un comando export como este:"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "xyoVQomURZwuTB5boQrlub4ZPDlymuoXG6mXQ+7BUCc=",
    "originContent": " - `export MARS_INSTALL_DIR=/path/to/mars`",
    "translatedContent": " - `export MARS_INSTALL_DIR=/path/to/mars`"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "HKkmwIKkh/ieiMP2kW0j8EIg0q9OdFbnoA5PMx2tBTQ=",
    "originContent": "If you forget `--recurse-submodules` then run:",
    "translatedContent": "Si olvida `--recurse-submodules` entonces ejecute:"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "GnqY646LgalmrjYiy85EoCEcEmDQjPBNa5an3o9PfYI=",
    "originContent": " - `git submodule init && git submodule update`",
    "translatedContent": " - `git submodule init && git submodule update`"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "84w5X0UhmKu5AWgu8jm6Dmb3R0585SU1RR0SCOlDrBM=",
    "originContent": "Also, it is **highly recommended** to use something like `-j8`, replacing the 8 with",
    "translatedContent": "Además, se **recomienda encarecidamente** usar algo como `-j8`, reemplazando el 8 por"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "7WfcRBwzjomnwk+053ZqUDZx1BSxy4H9wp1ZCO9F5Oc=",
    "originContent": "the number of CPU cores you have. I've run into weird unexplainable problems with `-j`",
    "translatedContent": "el número de núcleos de CPU que tenga. Me he encontrado con problemas extraños e inexplicables con `-j`"
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "63uDJm8KZoBmVETEewfF/9CR4jfvl+hDJ46YQn5v0Rk=",
    "originContent": "by itself, so please specify a number.",
    "translatedContent": "por sí solo, así que por favor especifique un número."
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
